title: 03/09/21 DPS Hour 2 Julius Erving and Dan Orlovsky
itunes:title: 03/09/21 DPS Hour 2 Julius Erving and Dan Orlovsky
description:
Julius Erving tells Dan how he got the name Dr. J. Julius says that he is 71 years old and has not dunked since he was 63. Dan Orlovsky tells Dan that this was a big swing and miss for the Cowboys. Orlovsky says it was a good day for Dak Prescott.
